item.description:
Webhook Receiver Pattern (`POST /api/v1/webhooks/{provider}/{event}`) com HMAC-SHA256 + `Idempotency-Key` + Outbox stub. Preparação para Epic 15 (Pix) e Epic 5 (KYC callbacks Celcoin).

**Headers obrigatórios:**
- `Idempotency-Key`: UUID/string única por evento
- `X-Webhook-Signature`: hex lowercase do HMAC-SHA256(secret, payload)

**Como gerar a assinatura no Postman (Pre-request Script):**
```js
const secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('webhookSecret');
const body = pm.request.body.raw;
const hmac = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();
pm.request.headers.upsert({key: 'X-Webhook-Signature', value: hmac});
```

