item.description:
Webhook publico (sem JWT) do provider de assinatura digital. Path param `{provider}` aceita `clicksign` (whitelist). HMAC SHA-256 via header `Content-Hmac: sha256=<hex>` (Clicksign) ou alias `X-Webhook-Signature: <hex>` (formato generico). Idempotency-Key opcional — quando ausente, derivado via SHA-256(provider:payload). Body max 64KB (defesa DoS). Outbox compartilhado da Sprint 4 (`webhook_event_log`) + UNIQUE `(envelope_id, id_evento_externo)` na `evento_assinatura` garantem dedup natural.

**Secret HMAC**: variavel `clicksignWebhookSecret` (preencher localmente; env `APP_WEBHOOK_SECRET_CLICKSIGN`).

**Pre-request script** (gera Content-Hmac):
```js
const secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('clicksignWebhookSecret');
const body = pm.request.body.raw;
const hmac = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();
pm.request.headers.upsert({key: 'Content-Hmac', value: 'sha256=' + hmac});
```

